Invocation Name: bakery weekly specials
des:
At NUM Gourmet Desserts we are THE DESSERT SPECIALISTS! Gluten-Free, Sugar-Free & Oh so Keto. You can find the best tasting, highest quality desserts that will make your tastebuds sing and leave you wondering how these are these "keto". Shipping nationwide all you have to do is pick what you like and we will ship it right to your door.

NUM Gourmet Desserts is the perfect Gluten-free, Sugar-Free, and Keto Friendly bakery that specializes in taking America's favorite desserts and turning them into a healthier alternative for people who have nutritional restrictions or choose to live a certain lifestyle.
